<Container>
<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center" id="hero">
    <div class="row items-center py-5 md:pb-20 md:pt-10">
        <div class="text-center space-y-3">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-medium leading-none md:text-6xl">Crowdfunding for <br> musicians <br> on decentralized infrastructure</h1>
            <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-xl font-normal leading-7 sm:mb-12">We've created a two way conduit for music lovers to support their favorite musicians and for musicians to give back to their fans.</p>
            <a class="px-9 py-5 bg-zinc-900 hover:bg-white text-white hover:text-black border rounded-2xl gap-2.5 inline-flex" href="/#protocol">
                <h2 class="text-center text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discover the protocol</h2>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

